QuestData.Title: Lumber for Lakeshire
QuestData.Description:
Magistrate Solomon requested a bundle of wood for his hearth. However, he's been too busy to come by and retrieve it.
If you wouldn't mind running it down to him at the town hall, I'm sure he'd appreciate it.
QuestData.LogDescription: Bring the Bundle of Lumber to Magistrate Solomon at the Lakeshire Town Hall.
